BIOS
	hardware configuration
	boot device order

SysV reboot
	shutdown -r now
	telinit 6

init systems used within Linux systems
	upstart
	sysv init
	systemd

file in the /proc filesystem lists parameters passed from the bootloader to the kernel
	cmdline, /proc/cmdline

lspci command display about the system hardware
	Device IRQ settings
	PCI bus speed
	Device vendor identification


